  14,12,Why nos non trust DEUS when He guided nos noster paths? Nos steadfastly persevere in the face de tuus persecution. In DEUS totus trusters trust
  14,13,Those disbelieved dictus to their messengers Nos perfecit banish vos ex noster cataster vos revert noster religionis. Their Dominus inspired them Nos inevitably annihilate transgressors
